	Counteract the side effect of the fix for bug #1614540. Improvements
	to png image format support detection. Make notebook tabs resizable.
	* WinXP-Blue/WinXP-Blue.tcl:
	Updates to work with Tile 0.8.X. Also allow using different libraries
	that support PNG images. Fix bug #1825571

